name: Blue Notes
description:
“blue notes” is a print of an original piece which was drawn in black ink then digitally enhanced.
The final artwork is digitally printed on high quality paper with a nice white border for framing. 
Image Size 5” x 8.5” Actual size with border 7” x 10” 
This artwork will come to you signed and sealed in a polythene bag.
